{"tid":1099102,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"周國腎係香港樂壇都好有影響力","createTime":"2019-04-09T14:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T11:19:33.000Z","uid":201665,"like":56,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09b5094a531022b095b9c4e8ba359b4c51c8e0c3","tid":1099102,"uid":201665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"腎仔作為一個唱作歌手<br />\n係香港入面都算幾出色同幾有影響力<br />\n出過咁多首歌 無幾首係無咩人唔鐘意<br />\n而且亦都有好多首街知巷聞既歌<br />\n例如黃金入球 地下街 不敵<br />\n我敢講 現今香港樂壇入面<br />\n除左張敬軒同埋容祖兒<br />\n腎仔一定可以屌贏所有其他垃圾歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且到依家都咁唱得<br />\n<br />\n香港樂壇欠腎仔一個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想等到佢終有一日係紅館立足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢既live真係麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢唱既時候都可以帶起現場氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚正呀腎仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c09633f96913edbeeddc0dee1328f611c28fa0","tid":1099102,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:17:52.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cd7cb0632949f792af28e8f9fa1da61be4f35a","tid":1099102,"uid":201665,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:18:47.000Z","msg":"好想做腎仔老婆 瘋狂比佢地下街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde353f953eaa364b5c103fac0c4e72edf572b1a","tid":1099102,"uid":201665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"好想次次去有佢既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fac793808a98f5050fd44aa68ef0de17f1ec825","tid":1099102,"uid":34154,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"兩年前佢開銀河鐵道之夜，唱live已經有飛躍嘅進步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlive 嘅有時, 重逢, 星塵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1213e2949e89d811f128b7a10aa61b33c89e605","tid":1099102,"uid":201665,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fac793808a98f5050fd44aa68ef0de17f1ec825","tid":1099102,"uid":34154,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"兩年前佢開銀河鐵道之夜，唱live已經有飛躍嘅進步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlive 嘅有時, 重逢, 星塵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"離一離題 佢個次既黃金入球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8288166620a2ac7904931e2035b7f7ff293e531","tid":1099102,"uid":5369,"like":6,